Sinethemba Thethwayo, 16, from the Holy Family College has been volunteering at the Denis Hurley Center for four years.

The grade 11 pupil is passionate about helping others. “Whatever you do, whatever your age, race or beliefs you can make a huge difference in someone else’s life by just helping them out in the most simplest ways.”














